0.1-pre-5:
- add getopt.c for building under windows
- add some more information to the maildir name
- store fingerprint of servers certificate in .aardmail/somewhat; warn if the fingerprint
  does not match; enable checking of the servers certificate using a local ca-file

0.2-pre-1:
- add fetchmail frontend
- add a sane sendmail (with manpage)

0.2-pre-2:
- make sendmail/smtpc-combination suitable for multiuser-systems

0.2-pre-3:
- use the now integrated cram-md5-foo
- add base64, plain auth

0.2-pre-4:
- add pop3d
- add auth using client certificates to pop3c (works with smtpc, not much to be done for pop3c)
